quote_last:
“Darling, do you think they’ll figure out it was a ruse?”
“Who knows.” He looked up from stoking the fireplace, where nothing but embers remained. “Tanzan Mino may be a genius, but the rest of his Yakuza hoods are not exactly rocket scientists.”
title: Project Daedalus
author: Thomas Hoover

quote_first: They made an unostentatious exit from their coach, finding themselves, when the express had rolled on into the west, upon a station platform in a foreign city at
quote_last: o’clock in the morning — but at length without their shadow.
title: The Black Bag
author: Louis Joseph Vance
